headline: Otis to Power Mobility in The Westin Residences, Tallest Residential Tower in Penang, Malaysia
summary: Otis (NYSE: OTIS), the world's leading elevator and escalator manufacturing, installation and service company, will install cutting edge technologies and smart, connected solutions that power vertical mobility for the Westin Residence and Hotel by Macrovest Sdn. Bhd. (VST Group), a leading developer in Malaysia.
